         <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; line-height:115%; font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">&#xa0;</span></p>
         <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; line-height:115%; font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Arial">Sebagai bahan pertimbangan kami lampirkan</span><span style="font-family:Arial">:</span></p>
