         <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; line-height:115%; font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Arial">2. Salinan/fotokopi SIUP-MB</span><span style="font-family:Arial">/SKMB</span></p>
         <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; line-height:115%; font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Arial">3. Salinan/fotokopi ITPMB</span></p>
         <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; line-height:115%; font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Arial">4. </span><span style="font-family:Arial">Gambar denah lokasi Toko/Perusahaan</span></p>
         <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; line-height:115%; font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Arial">5</span><span style="font-family:Arial">. Gambar tata ruang dan bangunan Toko/Perusahaan</span></p>
         <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; line-height:115%; font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Arial">6. Salinan/fotokopi Nomor Pokok Wajib Pajak (NPWP)</span></p>
         <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; line-height:115%; font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Arial">7. Salinan/fotokopi Kartu Identitas/pengenal diri </span></p>
